4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:313.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न वेठितसीसस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:314.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ६७। ओगुण्ठितसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:314.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न ओगुण्ठितसीसस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:315.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ६८। छमासिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:315.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न छमायं निसीदित्वा आसने निसिन्नस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:316.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ६९। नीचासनसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:316.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न नीचे आसने निसीदित्वा उच्चे आसने निसिन्नस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:317.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ७०। ठितासिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:317.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न ठिता निसिन्नस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:318.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ७१। पच्छतोगच्छन्तीसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:318.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न पच्छतो गच्छन्ती पुरतो गच्छन्तस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:319.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ७२। उप्पथेनगच्छन्तीसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:319.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न उप्पथेन गच्छन्ती पथेन गच्छन्तस्स अगिलानस्स धम्मं देसेस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:320.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ७३। ठिताउच्चारसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:320.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न ठिता अगिलाना उच्चारं वा पस्सावं वा करिस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:321.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ७४। हरितेउच्चारसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:321.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न हरिते अगिलाना उच्चारं वा पस्सावं वा खेळं वा करिस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:322.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिय ७५। उदकेउच्चारसिक्खापदं </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:322.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">न उदके अगिलाना उच्चारं वा पस्सावं वा खेळं वा करिस्सामीति सिक्खा करणीया। </span></span></span></p><p class="endsection"><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:322.2"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">पादुकवग्गो सत्तमो। </span></span></span></p><hr><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:323.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा खो, अय्यायो, सेखिया धम्मा। </span></span></span><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:323.2"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">तत्थाय्यायो पुच्छामि, कच्चित्थ परिसुद्धा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:323.3"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">दुतियम्पि पुच्छामि, कच्चित्थ परिसुद्धा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:323.4"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">ततियम्पि पुच्छामि, कच्चित्थ परिसुद्धा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:323.5"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">परिसुद्धेत्थाय्यायो, तस्मा तुण्ही, एवमेतं धारयामीति। </span></span></span></p><p class="endsection"><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:323.6"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सेखिया निट्ठिता। </span></span></span></p><h2><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:324.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथा </span></span></span></h2><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:324.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">इमे खो पनाय्यायो, सत्त अधिकरणसमथा धम्मा उद्देसं आगच्छन्ति। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:325.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ १ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:325.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सम्मुखाविनयो दातब्बो। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:326.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ २ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:326.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">सतिविनयो दातब्बो। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:327.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ ३ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:327.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अमूळ्हविनयो दातब्बो। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:328.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ ४ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:328.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">पटिञ्ञाय कारेतब्बं। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:329.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ ५ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:329.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">येभुय्यसिका। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:330.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ ६ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:330.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">तस्सपापियसिका। </span></span></span></p><h4><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:331.0"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथ ७ </span></span></span></h4><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:331.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">तिणवत्थारकोति। </span></span></span></p><hr><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:332.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा खो अय्यायो सत्त अधिकरणसमथा धम्मा। </span></span></span><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:332.2"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">तत्थाय्यायो पुच्छामि, कच्चित्थ परिसुद्धा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:332.3"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">दुतियम्पि पुच्छामि, कच्चित्थ परिसुद्धा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:332.4"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">ततियम्पि पुच्छामि, कच्चित्थ परिसुद्धा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:332.5"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">परिसुद्धेत्थाय्यायो, तस्मा तुण्ही, एवमेतं धारयामीति। </span></span></span></p><p class="endsection"><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:332.6"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">अधिकरणसमथा निट्ठिता। </span></span></span></p><p><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.1"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठं खो अय्यायो निदानं </span></span></span><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.2"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा अट्ठ पाराजिका धम्मा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.3"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा सत्तरस सङ्घादिसेसा धम्मा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.4"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा तिंस निस्सग्गिया पाचित्तिया धम्मा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.5"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा छसट्ठि सता पाचित्तिया धम्मा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.6"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा अट्ठ पाटिदेसनीया धम्मा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.7"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा सेखिया धम्मा, </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.8"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">उद्दिट्ठा सत्त अधिकरणसमथा धम्मा। </span></span></span><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.9"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">एत्तकं तस्स भगवतो सुत्तागतं सुत्तपरियापन्नं अन्वद्धमासं उद्देसं आगच्छति। </span></span></span> <span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.10"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">तत्थ सब्बाहेव समग्गाहि सम्मोदमानाहि अविवदमानाहि सिक्खितब्बन्ति। </span></span></span></p> <p class="endsection"><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.11"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">वित्थारुद्देसो चतुत्थो। </span></span></span></p><p class="endsutta"><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.12"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">भिक्खुनिपातिमोक्खं निट्ठितं। </span></span></span></p><p class="namo"><span class="segment" id="pli-tv-bi-pm:333.13"><span class="root" lang="pli" translate="no"><span class="text devanagari-script">नमो तस्स भगवतो अरहतो सम्मासम्बुद्धस्स </span></span></span></p></article>
